      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SIR RICO (1) racing well without winning, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd over 300m at this track beaten 2.25 lengths (17.25) behind Chaotic Boy in a TG1-4W on May 27. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Well placed and gets his chance. ELLSWORTH (5) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing third (17.44) in a Grade 6 at this track. Hard to beat again. VISTA CADMIUM (7) copped a check in the run last time and never threatened when eighth (31.93) in a Special conditions race at Angle Park Night. Key player if finds best. TREE TOWN (3) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
